      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Hadoop<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> (the \"Query\" workload): Provides reliable data storage with <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>HDFS<ept id=\"p2\">](#HDFS)</ept>, and a simple <bpt id=\"p3\">[</bpt>MapReduce<ept id=\"p3\">](#mapreduce)</ept> programming model to process and analyze data in parallel."
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hbase.apache.org/\"&gt;</ph>HBase<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> (the \"NoSQL\" workload): A NoSQL database built on Hadoop that provides random access and strong consistency for large amounts of unstructured and semi-structured data - potentially billions of rows times millions of columns.",
