      "pos": [
        4816,
        4882
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a  target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://storm.incubator.apache.org/\"&gt;</ph>Apache Storm<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> (the \"Stream\" workload): A distributed, real-time computation system for processing large streams of data fast.",
