      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Ambari<ept id=\"p2\">](#ambari)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Cluster provisioning, management, and monitoring."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        5481,
        5588
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Avro<ept id=\"p2\">](#avro)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> (Microsoft .NET Library for Avro): Data serialization for the Microsoft .NET environment."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        5592,
        5710
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Hive &amp; HCatalog<ept id=\"p2\">](#hive)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Structured Query Language (SQL)-like querying, and a table and storage management layer."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
