      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Phoenix<ept id=\"p2\">](#phoenix)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Relational database layer over HBase."
    },
